60|$|He {{glanced at}} his watch, relit his pipe, and relapsed once more into sombre silence. Julia's {{thoughts}} went flitting away. <b>She</b> <b>closed</b> <b>her</b> <b>eyes</b> <b>and</b> leaned back. She had only one fear now. Would he find out! He was thick enough, in his way, but he was no fool, and he was already coarsely jealous.|$|E
